Ganache
Open Ganache ETH
Show key -> First -> Copy Private Key

Open MetaMask
Create Account
Accounts->Add Wallet->Import an Account->Paste Private Key->Import
click on imported account->click menu on right corner with three line ->Networks->Add Custom Network

Network Name - Ganache
Add RPC  URL -> Open Ganache Window -> Copy RPC Server link (Most of time:HTTP://127.0.0.1:7545)->Paste->Add Url
Chain ID -> open Ganache Window ->copy Network id (Most of time 5777 if error than try 1337)->paste->Add
Currency Symbol-ETH
Save

Now Imported Account would show Value if imported properly
